<th align="left" width="100"><a href="/wiki/Simplified_Chinese" title="Simplified Chinese" class="mw-redirect">Simp.</a></th>
<th align="left" width="130">Total Speakers</th>
<th align="left" width="180">Notes</th>
</tr>
