<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Chinese_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: Dictionaries">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Dictionaries</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i>ABC Chinese-English Comprehensive Dictionary</i>. Editor: John de Francis. (2003) University of Hawai’i Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/082482766X" class="internal">ISBN 0-8248-2766-X</a>.</li>
<li><i>ABC Etymological Dictionary of Old Chinese</i>. Axel Schuessler. 2007. University of Hawai’i Press, Honolulu. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780824829759" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-8248-2975-9</a>.</li>
</ul>
